      "text": "私の体にもっとセクシー成分が増量されるまで\n延期にしてほしいんです……二十歳までには必ず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My body… well‚ I want to wait until it's more \"sexy\"…\nUntil it has more appeal… like until when I get twenty years old…",
